This Privacy Policy outlines the data practices for Spell Rise,
a mobile application developed by Tiitus Koski.
We prioritize transparency and user privacy, and we want to ensure that you understand how your information is handled within the app.

Information We Collect:
  We do not collect or store any personal data about our users.
  The app solely stores game progress data locally on your device.

Data Storage:
  Game progress data is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to any external servers.
  We do not have access to, nor do we store, any personally identifiable information.

Third-Party Services:
  The app does not integrate with any third-party services that would result in the collection of personal data.

Changes to Privacy Policy:
  Any updates or changes to our privacy practices will be reflected in this Privacy Policy.

Contact Us:
  If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at tiitus.koski@gmail.com

By using Spell Rise, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. 
We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates. 
Thank you for choosing Spell Rise.
